Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
I came all the way here just to shop! But there's
nothing to buy! This is an outrage!

<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
I found something great, but they were all sold
out! Someone needs to fix that supply and
demand problem.

<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
I bought a lot of good stuff cheap! Time to go
rake in the profits!

<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
This town's opened up a lot of doors for me,
financially speaking. Thank you very much!

<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
Ouch. I took another loss... Wish someone
would've talked me out of that last deal.

<NAME_MOB_IRINA>
Every so often, I make just the right find at the
right time. That's why I could never quit this job!
